<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-1785] Problem With MarkupBuilder In Static Method</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-1785</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am seeing odd behavior when I try to use a MarkupBuilder in a static method.  The following fails with a MissingMethodException (waba is the missing method):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Foo.groovy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Foo {

  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; void main(args) {
	def xml = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; groovy.xml.MarkupBuilder()
	def configMap = [name:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;Jeff&apos;&lt;/span&gt;]

	xml.foo {
		configMap.each { key, value -&amp;gt;
			waba(name:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bar&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
		}
	}
  }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following seems to work fine:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Foo.groovy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Foo {

  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; void main(args) {
	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Foo() 
  }
  
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; Foo() {
	def xml = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; groovy.xml.MarkupBuilder()
	def configMap = [name:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;Jeff&apos;&lt;/span&gt;]

	xml.foo {
		configMap.each { key, value -&amp;gt;
			waba(name:&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bar&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
		}
	}
  }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
